OL,3,CBuses back under local control for
OL,4,Cfirst time in 40 years
OL,6,FGreater Manchester has become the
OL,7,Ffirst area in England in four decades
OL,8,Fto bring its bus services under local
OL,9,Fcontrol.
OL,11,FThe shift, completed as part of the
OL,12,Fregion's Bee Network, affects 577
OL,13,Froutes and 1,600 buses, which handle
OL,14,Fover 160 million journeys annually.
OL,16,FTransport for Greater Manchester
OL,17,F(TfGM) says it hopes the move will
OL,18,F"deliver a more reliable, affordable,
OL,19,Fand environmentally friendly public
OL,20,Ftransport that better serves its
OL,21,Fcommunities".
