OL,3,CBuses back under local control for
OL,4,Cfirst time in 40 years
OL,6,FIt said the new system promises
OL,7,Fimproved connections and punctuality,
OL,8,Fand according to TfGM, the reliability
OL,9,Fof buses in areas already under local
OL,10,Fcontrol has risen from around 69% to
OL,11,Fover 80%.
OL,13,FAround to 75 routes now have earlier,
OL,14,Flater, and more frequent services, as
OL,15,Fwell as night buses.
