OL,3,CBuses back under local control for
OL,4,Cfirst time in 40 years
OL,6,FA #2 cap on single tickets has been
OL,7,Fintroduced across the network and,
OL,8,Ffrom March, a contactless payment
OL,9,Fsystem will calculate the lowest daily
OL,10,For weekly fare for bus and tram
OL,11,Fjourneys.
OL,13,FHundreds of new buses are expected to
OL,14,Fbe introduced as part of the Bee
OL,15,FNetwork with, TfGM says, 52% of the
OL,16,Ffleet expected to be replaced by March
OL,17,F2025.
OL,19,FMayor Andy Burnham described the
OL,20,Ftransition as a significant moment for
OL,21,Fpublic transport in England.
