OL,6,F"Every community in Greater Manchester
OL,7,Fwill now be served by cheaper,
OL,8,Fcleaner, and greener buses," he said.
OL,10,F"This isn't just a win for passengers;
OL,11,Fit's an opportunity for economic
OL,12,Fgrowth, better connectivity, and a
OL,13,Fhigher quality of life.
OL,15,F"The re-regulation of buses has also
OL,16,Fled to job creation, with hundreds of
OL,17,Froles generated both in the operation
OL,18,Fof services and the manufacturing of
OL,19,Fnew buses.
