OL,6,FTransport advocates are watching
OL,7,FGreater Manchester's efforts closely
OL,8,Fas other regions consider similar
OL,9,Fchanges.
OL,11,FSecretary of State for Transport,
OL,12,FHeidi Alexander, described the Bee
OL,13,FNetwork as a "trailblazer" for the
OL,14,Frest of the country.
