OL,3,CBuses back under local control for
OL,4,Cfirst time in 40 years
OL,6,F"This Government has prioritised
OL,7,Fsupporting and improving bus networks
OL,8,Facross the country as we know how
OL,9,Fimportant they are for communities -
OL,10,Fbut for too long, too many people have
OL,11,Fsuffered from unreliable and
OL,12,Finfrequent services," she said.
OL,14,FDr Maya Singer Hobbs from the
OL,15,FInstitute for Public Policy Research
OL,16,F(IPPR) North said Greater Manchester's
OL,17,Fmodel demonstrates the potential
OL,18,Fbenefits of local control, including
OL,19,Fbetter environmental, social, and
OL,20,Feconomic outcomes.
