OL,6,FPlans are underway to integrate rail
OL,7,Fservices into the Bee Network by 2028,
OL,8,Fstarting with eight priority train
OL,9,Flines. Improvements to cycling and
OL,10,Fwalking infrastructure are also
OL,11,Fongoing, with over 117km of routes
OL,12,Falready delivered.
OL,14,FDame Sarah Storey, Greater
OL,15,FManchester's Active Travel
OL,16,FCommissioner, emphasized the need to
OL,17,Fmake walking and cycling safer and
OL,18,Fmore accessible.
